name: Danielle Marie
coverLetter:
Over the last year I traveled to Felton to work with a grower, going back and forth between home and California. 
My fiance and I have been Chefs for the last ten years. We work hard, and efficiently. 
We have a camper built out in our Tacoma, with two small well behaved dogs. Simply need a campground or place to park near by. We are very self-sufficient. Looking forward to improving in a new trade.
